  "bandName": "Blame It On Frank",
  "lyrics": {
    "22": "I can′t remember when I last felt this way\nI can't remember when the clouds and the rain couldn′t dull my day\nI can't remember having a feeling so fine\nI can't remember when you weren′t the one that was on my mind\nMaybe your smile\nOr maybe your style\nMakes me wanna\nWith you\nI can′t remember when I last felt this way\nI can't remember when the clouds and the rain couldn′t dull my day\nI can't remember having a feeling so fine\nI can′t remember when you weren't the one that was on my mind\nYou don′t have to try\nIt's all in your eyes\nMakes me wanna\nWith you\nI can't remember when I last felt this way\nI can′t remember when the clouds and the rain couldn′t dull my day\nI can't remember having a feeling so fine\nI can′t remember when you weren't the one that was on my mind\nMaybe your smile\nOr maybe your style\nMakes me wanna\nWith you"
